message.content:
[
    "The feeling of adrenaline coursing through your veins",
    "Watching a storm rage outside while you're safe and warm inside",
    "The rush of a near-death experience that makes you feel truly alive",
    "Listening to music so loud it drowns out your thoughts",
    "Exploring abandoned buildings and feeling like you're in a horror movie",
    "Tattoos that tell the story of your life without saying a word",
    "Walking alone at night and feeling the weight of your solitude",
    "The taste of whiskey burning down your throat",
    "The thrill of standing on the edge of a cliff and looking down",
    "The sound of breaking glass in a fit of rage",
    "The intoxicating scent of leather and cigarettes",
    "Feeling the sting of a fresh wound that reminds you you're human",
    "The chaos of a city that never sleeps",
    "The rush of doing something that terrifies you",
    "Wearing all black and feeling like a badass",
    "The twisted beauty of decay and destruction",
    "The power of a loud, angry scream that releases all your pent-up emotions",
    "The thrill of a forbidden love that consumes you",
    "The allure of danger that beckons you to take risks",
    "The high of staring death in the face and walking away unscathed",
    "The darkness inside you that sets you apart from the rest"
]
